title: HUMAN EVENTS DAILY: OCT 28 2021 - SHADE WAR UPDATE: FIRST LADY JILL BIDEN VS. VP KAMALA HARRIS.
description:
On today’s episode of Human Events Daily:  an update on the shade war between First Lady Jill Biden and Vice President Kamala Harris, Black Rock Inc. becomes the first global asset manager licensed to start a wholly owned onshore mutual fund business in China, Prosecutors say charges are on the table for Alec Baldwin, and people are given accidental Covid-19 Vaccine at an Army Base.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
